txt.en: The four Hobbits have been through a great deal on their journey to the gates of Mordor, but now are hailed as princes among the Men of Gondor. Swear your allegiance to Merry, Pippin, Frodo, and Sam, and you will join them in celebration, adventures, and a good number of hearty meals around the environs of Ithilien and Mordor.\n\nContacts: Merry or Golodhon can be found at Cirith Gorgor, just inside the ruins of the Black Gate.
